According to the conservation of momentum, the momentum of the composite particle is

$$
\begin{aligned}
& p_{M}=p=\sqrt{\left(3 m_{0}\right)^{2}-m_{0}^{2}}=\sqrt{8} m_{0} \\
& \quad E_{M}=\sqrt{p_{M}^{2}+M^{2}}=\sqrt{17+8} m_{0}=5 m_{0} \\
& \beta=\frac{p_{M}}{E_{M}}=\frac{2}{5} \sqrt{2}
\end{aligned}
$$

The velocity of the particle is

$$
v=\beta c=1.7 \times 10^{10} \, \text{(cm/s)}
