$$
\begin{aligned}
E_{\pi}^{\mathrm{th}} & =\frac{\left(2 m_{\mathrm{K}}+m_{\mathrm{n}}\right)^{2}-m_{\mathrm{p}}^{2}-m_{\pi}^{2}}{2 m_{\mathrm{p}}} \\
